  <brief_title>Endoscopic Placement of Metal Stent in Patients With Cancer-Related Bowel Obstruction</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Pilot Phase I/II Trial of Enteral Wallstents for Colonic Obstruction in the Setting of Malignancy</official_title>
